1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
("The Unique Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 21=

4
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,280
Why are you here?

5
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,680
What exactly are you trying to do?

6
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:41,200
Do you know she's terrified of fire?

7
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:43,120
Do you know you almost got her killed?

8
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,440
Because she has to remember.

9
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:49,840
What do you mean?

10
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,520
Because she forgot.

11
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,520
She forgot Ji Ran completely.

12
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:56,240
And you

13
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:58,520
aren't Ji Ran at all.

14
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:01,400
So Qiao Xiaomi has to remember.

15
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:04,240
She has to remember how my brother died.

16
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:07,560
Your brother?

17
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:09,000
That's right.

18
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:13,080
I'm Ji Ran's older brother.

19
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:18,720
Fine.

20
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,320
Now it's your turn.

21
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,080
Who exactly are you?

22
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,480
Qin Yu, save me!

23
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:29,920
Save me!

24
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,720
Qin Yu!

25
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,840
Qin Yu!

26
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,360
Save me!

27
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,400
That hurts so bad.

28
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:43,040
Those guys from the basketball team
really didn't hold back.

29
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:45,360
You're hurt?

30
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,840
Is it serious?

31
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,440
Who did it?

32
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:49,480
I'll go settle the score with them.

33
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:52,320
Got you.

34
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,520
I'm fine.

35
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:56,560
You lied to me again.

36
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,280
What if I'd really gone after them?

37
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,840
You can't.

38
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:03,760
Ye Xiaoduo,

39
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,200
even if something really happened,

40
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:06,000
you're not allowed to go.

41
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,440
Protecting people

42
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:09,840
is my job.

43
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:13,840
Looking down on me?

44
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,400
Why don't we spar a little?

45
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,280
It's not that I look down on you.

46
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,520
It's just that no matter what happens,

47
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:24,880
I won't let you get hurt.

48
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:28,320
I'll do all I can to protect you.

49
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:33,200
I don't need your protection.

50
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,880
From now on,

51
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,360
don't lie to me anymore.

52
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:39,720
Can you promise me that?

53
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,040
A promise is a promise.

54
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,320
If you can't keep it,

55
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,640
don't make it.

56
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:48,080
Okay.

57
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:49,040
Pinky swear.

58
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,720
Not even the King of Hell

59
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:56,200
could break this promise.

60
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,800
Ji Ran had an older brother?

61
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:03,240
Why did he never tell me?

62
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:07,280
My parents divorced years ago.

63
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,360
I took my stepfather's surname, Chen.

64
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,920
Four years ago,

65
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,760
we found Ji Ran

66
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,080
and wanted him to live with us.

67
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:18,120
He refused.

68
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,200
But not long after,

69
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:24,600
I heard he'd died in a fire.

70
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,960
That's why I had to get close
to Qiao Xiaomi.

71
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,880
To get the truth from her.

72
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,360
But she had you by her side.

73
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,600
Someone who looked
exactly like my brother.

74
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,640
Who are you, really?

75
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:40,440
I'm Qin Yu.

76
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:43,920
I just made myself look like Ji Ran.

77
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,120
Just like you,

78
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:48,400
I'm searching for the truth
from three years ago.

79
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:58,480
I...

80
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:01,080
I clearly

81
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:06,000
carried Xiaoduo out.

82
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:15,120
Ji Ran died.

83
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:17,560
Xiaoduo died.

84
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,640
What exactly happened?

85
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:30,880
(No one recognizes this face.)

86
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,680
(It can't do anything.)

87
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,840
(But with Ji Ran's face,)

88
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,720
(I can get close to the Qiao Family.)

89
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:41,240
(I can get close to Qiao Xiaomi,
the only one who may know the truth,)

90
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:44,360
(but lost her memory.)

91
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,720
Chen Yue,

92
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:56,240
if you really are Ji Ran's brother,

93
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,560
do you think Ji Ran would want

94
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,160
his brother to become someone
who doesn't care about others

95
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,960
and even hurts an innocent girl

96
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:05,880
just to find the truth?

97
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:09,600
Do you want to become that person?

98
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,320
Ji Ran's brother.

99
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:22,960
What if Qiao Xiaomi really did it?

100
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,000
What if she caused the fire?

101
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,000
She didn't.

102
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:26,880
It's okay.

103
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:28,920
We'll find out soon enough.

104
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,160
Chen Yue,

105
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,880
I'm warning you.

106
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:35,200
If anything happens to her,

107
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,680
I won't let you off.

108
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,120
Xiaoduo,

109
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,520
do you know why I

110
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:51,240
named you Xiaoduo?

111
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:55,240
Because Mom hoped

112
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,360
you would be like a little flower.

113
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:00,040
You don't have to shine the brightest,

114
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,720
but you must be resilient.

115
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:06,320
No matter whether life
brings storms or sunshine,

116
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,600
always be brave enough

117
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,840
to grow into

118
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:11,240
the person you're meant to be.

119
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,680
Xiaoduo,

120
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,280
from now on,

121
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,360
this is your home.

122
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:37,320
This is your sister, Xiaomi.

123
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:40,080
And that's your brother, Zhiwei.

124
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,280
Xiaomi,

125
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:43,600
you're the most sensible one.

126
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,920
Take good care of your sister.

127
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,000
Don't worry, Dad.

128
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:51,440
I'll take good care of her.

129
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,840
H-Hi, little sister.

130
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,320
Nice to meet you.

131
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:57,200
From now on,

132
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:58,880
we're family.

133
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,240
What a hick.

134
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:17,560
Never lived in a house this big before?

135
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:20,120
You think it's a skating rink?

136
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:21,680
Xiaoduo,

137
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:22,960
what happened?

138
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,360
Nothing, Dad.

139
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,760
She accidentally fell.

140
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:28,400
It's okay.

141
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,480
I can clean it up.

142
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:02,360
And you, little b*stard child.

143
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:04,040
Just like your mother,

144
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:06,320
always trying to steal
other people's men, huh?

145
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,280
Qiao Xiaomi!

146
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:09,560
The world doesn't revolve around you!

147
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:10,480
Get out of my way!

148
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:13,600
Do you realize
what happens if you do this?

149
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:14,920
I'd like to see

150
00:09:14,920 --> 00:09:16,120
what could possibly happen.

151
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:26,920
If you're Ye Xiaoduo,

152
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:29,280
every day of your future

153
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,960
will keep haunting me.

154
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:32,920
And in the end,

155
00:09:32,920 --> 00:09:34,080
it'll haunt you too.

156
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,240
But if

157
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,760
you're Qiao Xiaomi,

158
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,920
everything changes.

159
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,840
You'll be the rightful heir

160
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:46,160
to the Qiao Family.

161
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:48,080
And my only hope.

162
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,120
So,

163
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:51,640
since you've already lost your memory,

164
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:52,760
from now on,

165
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:55,480
live as Xiaomi.

166
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:57,400
For you,

167
00:09:58,160 --> 00:09:58,960
and for me,

168
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:01,040
it's the best option.

169
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,200
Next time you come home,

170
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,800
can you just go back to your doghouse?

171
00:10:36,520 --> 00:10:37,760
What a hick.

172
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:40,880
What, not happy?

173
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:43,000
I really don't get it.

174
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,560
Why do girls like you,
illegitimate daughters,

175
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:46,120
always so defiant?

176
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,360
Give it back!

177
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,000
Don't cry!

178
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,960
What right do you have to cry?

179
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:30,360
What right?

180
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,520
What right do you have to cry?

181
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:34,480
What right?

182
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:46,600
Don't you dare smile.

183
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:56,280
Wipe that smile off your face!

184
00:12:40,216 --> 00:12:42,286
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

185
00:12:42,286 --> 00:12:45,706
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

186
00:12:47,306 --> 00:12:49,196
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

187
00:12:49,196 --> 00:12:53,186
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

188
00:12:54,426 --> 00:12:56,286
♪Let me go, set me free♪

189
00:12:56,286 --> 00:13:00,326
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

190
00:13:00,866 --> 00:13:06,276
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

191
00:13:07,626 --> 00:13:09,766
♪The freedom you gave me♪

192
00:13:09,766 --> 00:13:13,406
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

193
00:13:14,666 --> 00:13:16,936
♪Love can barely move forward♪

194
00:13:16,936 --> 00:13:20,716
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

195
00:13:21,816 --> 00:13:24,056
♪The closeness I long for♪

196
00:13:24,056 --> 00:13:28,446
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

197
00:13:28,856 --> 00:13:30,676
♪I don't want to break free♪

198
00:13:30,676 --> 00:13:36,046
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪
